{"tid":647360,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[反全面粵教中] 家長「普教中」心聲：多一種語境是好事!","createTime":"2018-04-29T19:00:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-30T00:16:30.000Z","uid":53060,"like":2,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"399602478b5e36428fa263b7c3dd89b3868e208f","tid":647360,"uid":53060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T19:00:47.000Z","msg":"黃先生現有兩名兒子在德信就讀，長子亦是德信的畢業生。今年中三的長子和小五的次子，先後經歷過普教中和廣教中，他指<span style=\"color: red;\">兩人的中文科成績，都以高小在廣教中下較為優秀</span>。「初小用普教中，他們的分數一般是『8字頭』，但高小<span style=\"color: red;\">轉用廣教中後，就躍升至『9字頭』</span>。我估計，有些複雜概念，例如寫作的修辭技巧等，老師用廣東話解釋，他們會吸收得好一些。」<br />\n<br />\n不過，黃先生卻<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不贊成德信下學年全校轉回廣教中</span></strong>，「我認為在孩子年紀小時，製造多一種語境，讓他們接觸多一種語言，是一件好事，反正初小沒有呈分試的壓力，分數高低，不太重要。但高小因為要面對升中選校，成績高低很重要，這時就適合用廣教中」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://happypama.mingpao.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/847e119ea51125baaef935b3ef5672c5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhappypama.mingpao.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F04%2F847e119ea51125baaef935b3ef5672c5.jpg&h=bd9da69b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黃先生（圖中）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://happypama.mingpao.com/%E8%BC%95%E9%AC%86%E5%8D%87%E5%AD%B8/%E5%AD%B8%E7%BF%92%E7%AB%B6%E6%8A%80%E5%A0%B4/%E6%99%AE%E6%95%99%E4%B8%AD%E5%AE%B6%E9%95%B7%E5%BF%83%E8%81%B2%EF%BC%9A%E5%A4%9A%E4%B8%80%E7%A8%AE%E8%AA%9E%E5%A2%83%E6%98%AF%E5%A5%BD%E4%BA%8B/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhappypama.mingpao.com%2F%25E8%25BC%2595%25E9%25AC%2586%25E5%258D%2587%25E5%25AD%25B8%2F%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%25BF%2592%25E7%25AB%25B6%25E6%258A%2580%25E5%25A0%25B4%2F%25E6%2599%25AE%25E6%2595%2599%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E9%2595%25B7%25E5%25BF%2583%25E8%2581%25B2%25EF%25BC%259A%25E5%25A4%259A%25E4%25B8%2580%25E7%25A8%25AE%25E8%25AA%259E%25E5%25A2%2583%25E6%2598%25AF%25E5%25A5%25BD%25E4%25BA%258B%2F&d=NuYyARMr%2BTr6a%2FgzurVG3r%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=82586bfe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhappypama